snippet.title: Thanks, Come Again Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Our next title, in conjunction with Leaf Let and the Cartomancy Anthology.

Thanks, Come Again

A game about the day-to-day of a simple shopkeeper and their complex wares. Try not to give too much of yourself away.

Wishlist Cartomancy on Steam, out August 9th: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1869870/The_Cartomancy_Anthology/
